":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">犯法就係犯法</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihtF15YfWDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DihtF15YfWDw&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=069214a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihtF15YfWDw</a><br />\n<br />\n根據 第210章《盜竊罪條例》 第18C條 ， 不付款而離去是刑事罪行。 當一個人有不誠實意圖，想在收到貨品後或享用服務後逃避付款，就屬於犯罪。 ... 如果任何人收到貨品或享用服務後，本來應該付款，但他/ 她有不誠實意圖去逃避付款，並且沒有付錢就離開，他/ 她已經干犯不付款而離去的罪名。"},{"pid":"163af98f4f8d9ecfb2e6af861208b215e030d29e","tid":2032824,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b945e31db097c5c77bafa8e601adf37069c50ee6","tid":2032824,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbdf9410c384f12af42a404a4d313aa5b4847d1","tid":2032824,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cedb8a918347866b2eba93f8755e7c2ef78bce","tid":2032824,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla